    "title": "Now Hiring Software Engineer at ISRO Advisory Limited",
    "description": "ISRO Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Jaipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout ISRO Advisory Limited:\nISRO Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ISRO Advisory Limited!",
